      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project or a budget-friendly starter? This vehicle is ready for a dedicated new owner who isn't afraid of a little hard work! While it shows significant wear and will require some mechanical attention and bodywork to get back to its best, it's a fantastic opportunity to own a car at a very accessible price point. Grab your tools and bring this one back to life!",
