      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for all your weekend adventures? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid shape, runs super smoothly, and has been really well-loved. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, this beauty won't let you down. Come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
