    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS timing. This example retains its high-revving character with a crisp 8,000 RPM redline and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014and the M-Variable differential lock provides exceptional traction through the apex. Suspension geometry remains true with upgraded bushings for improved turn-in. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, its thermal management and compression numbers are within spec, making it an ideal candidate for spirited weekend use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
