    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride in ownership, offering a harmonious blend of performance and comfort. The exterior finish maintains a deep, reflective gloss, with only minor, unavoidable stone chips on the lower front bumper that do not detract from its impressive curb appeal. Inside, the cabin remains a serene environment; the premium upholstery is clean and intact, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s seat. All interior electronics, including the infotainment system and climate control, operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, backed by a comprehensive service log that includes a recent fluid flush and a multi-point inspection. The tires have significant tread depth remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This car has been driven thoughtfully and maintained proactively, making it a turnkey option for a buyer who values both reliability and aesthetic quality.",
      "price": 36800.0,
